column5: Yah get back home from spending the day on the water. Your hungry and your feet are sore... here's your solution!  HH
Oooooookay... Until I saw the link I thought this was one of the weirder combinations I had ever seen - St. John Fish Sandwiches and Antiques

That man is a genius!   When I was a kid, there was a place called Aqua-java at the local plaza.  It was an aquarium pet shop that also sold coffee, sandwiches and donuts.  It closed down after 3 months.
Now that guy is funny but I'll stick to my Sue's solution for when I come home tired and hungry  I haven't been coming home for over 30 years for nothing!!!!!!
Yah gotta love the man's spirit and enthusiasm. HH
He's MOTIVATED! MOTIVATED! MOTIVATED! MOTIVATED!ï»¿  I can't stop watching this!
Crap, I thought he was talking about MY Spirit and motovation LOL!
Barbara was asking what has been going on at your home for the last 30 years..............
Now that I think of it Big Cliff, I guess I did mean BOTH of you! LOL HH
